{"tid":873360,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【第廿五孝】38歲仔心痛阿媽俾人打 返公園「尋仇」打躁底阿姨","createTime":"2018-10-23T11:24:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-24T12:12:40.000Z","uid":122,"like":590,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":93,"replies":[{"pid":"bbbc286a378d93fba7b527d4a232ba15a538c319","tid":873360,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T11:24:28.000Z","msg":"【冤冤相報】38歲仔心痛阿媽俾人打 返公園「尋仇」打躁底阿姨<br />\n<br />\n下午2時許，一名58歲姓鄧女子在將軍澳尚德邨公園內，與一名60歲姓鍾女子發生爭執，其間遭對方打傷眼部。鄧女不甘受辱，憤憤不平下返家向其38歲姓金兒子哭訴，金男聞訊後折返現場，用硬物襲擊鍾女頭部，有男途人見狀上前制止，但被打傷耳部。警方接報到場調查，拘捕傷人的金男，而鍾女亦涉嫌普通毆打被捕，而鄧女及男途人事後則送院治理。"},{"pid":"25929f6f2bc21e466d0526230b97ac695baf4ad3","tid":873360,"uid":122,"like":2,"dislike":24,"score":-22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T13:00:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29640c218baf4b16f6417d32d139a79ed9772be2","tid":873360,"uid":60408,"like":1468,"dislike":3,"score":1465,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T13:14:20.000Z","msg":"老母比人打我覺得幫拖係人之常情丫"},{"pid":"c068fb99694120d5ec00e1122a611b97ab38ee57","tid":873360,"uid":26976,"like":170,"dislike":3,"score":167,"quote":{"pid":"29640c218baf4b16f6417d32d139a79ed9772be2","tid":873360,"uid":60408,"like":1468,"dislike":3,"score":1465,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T13:14:20.000Z","msg":"老母比人打我覺得幫拖係人之常情丫"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T13:15:27.000Z","msg":"係"},{"pid":"5fab3d663b047315c934a39836d53fb9e3770cc1","tid":873360,"uid":199456,"like":393,"dislike":10,"score":383,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T13:16:15.000Z","msg":"如果我在場 會幫手打9個男途人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8041c49bbfd28352a64cc86b6eeea627cb0ce6c0","tid":873360,"uid":2567,"like":357,"dislike":8,"score":349,"quote":{"pid":"5fab3d663b047315c934a39836d53fb9e3770cc1","tid":873360,"uid":199456,"like":393,"dislike":10,"score":383,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T13:16:15.000Z","msg":"如果我在場 會幫手打9個男途人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"c